# Debug & Deployment Tools

## Backend (Poetry scripts from `backend/` directory)

```bash
poetry run service-deploy <service>                    # Deploy CloudFormation stacks
poetry run service-build <service>                     # Build Lambda zip package
poetry run service-update <service> -y                 # Update Lambda code only
poetry run dump-raw                                    # Dump DynamoDB table (raw)
poetry run dump-as-tree                                # Dump DynamoDB table (tree view)
```

## Backend Debug Scripts

```bash
python scripts/cloudwatch_mgmt.py dump-logs <lambda-name> --hours 2   # Lambda logs
python scripts/mockuser_mgmt.py                                        # Create mock user
python scripts/secretsmanager_mgmt.py                                  # Manage secrets
python scripts/dynamodb_mgmt.py                                        # DynamoDB management
python scripts/apigateway_dump.sh                                      # API Gateway dump
```

## Lambda Names for Log Queries

- `auth-platform`, `auth-jwt-authorizer`
- `user-profile-mgmt`, `user-media-mgmt`, `user-media-processing`, `user-location-mgmt`
- `feed-query`
- `chat-websocket-mgmt`, `chat-websocket-msgs`

## Frontend (from `frontend/` directory)

```bash
npm run dev          # Start dev server (Vite + HTTPS via mkcert)
npm run build        # Production build
npm run preview      # Preview production build
```

## Code Locations

- Backend Lambda handlers: `backend/src/services/<service>/aws_lambdas/<lambda>/lambda_function.py`
- Backend shared code: `backend/src/common/aws_lambdas/core/`
- Backend CloudFormation: `backend/src/services/<service>/cloudformation/`
- Frontend API clients: `frontend/src/api/`
- Frontend contexts: `frontend/src/contexts/`
- Frontend pages: `frontend/src/pages/`
